item.title: CVE-2021-26116|2024-08-03T20:19:20.055Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortiauthenticator
item.description: An improper neutralization of special elements used in an OS command vulnerability in the command line interpreter of FortiAuthenticator before 6.3.1 may allow an authenticated attacker to execute unauthorized commands via specifically crafted arguments to existing commands.
